The CAD models and STEP files in this directory were obtained from the
NIST MBE PMI Validation and Conformance Testing project:
https://www.nist.gov/ctl/smart-connected-systems-division/smart-connected-manufacturing-systems-group/mbe-pmi-validation

These files were created by the National Institute of Standards and
Technology (NIST), a U.S. federal government agency. Pursuant to
Title 17 United States Code Section 105, works produced by U.S.
government employees in the course of their official duties are not
subject to copyright protection in the United States and are in the
public domain.

These files may be freely redistributed and used without restriction.
